8. Breach of Conduct
If a problem occurs within the team, the following process will be followed:
Step	Action
Step 1	Discuss the issue privately between team members.
Step 2	Agree on a solution or adjustment.
Step 3	Record the outcome in the meeting tracker.
Step 4	If unresolved, escalate to the module lecturer.
